Adjectives
-------------
The order of using adjectives:

quantity-- opinion-- size-- age-- shape-- color-- origin-- material-- purpose
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
two	|tasty	   |big  |new   |long	|red	|Italian |silk	  |sports
three	|lovely	   |smal |old	|round	|blue	|French	 |wooden  |coffee

Example:
I've got three cozy big old purple bedrooms.
Wonderful old red flower.



